title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“I'm sorry I never got to meet him while he was alive.” [Leonard Maltin on Andy Devine, from Entertainment Tonight, TV program, 20 February 1989. Submitted by Emilio Bernal Labrada, Falls Church, Virginia.]
